#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgovernance-badges.md:1
msgid "Governance Badges"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgovernance-badges.md:3
msgid ""
"DMN cards in the Available DMNs panel and the Chain Composer display a "
"validation badge when the DMN has been formally reviewed by a competent "
"Dutch government authority."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgovernance-badges.md:7
msgid "Interpreting badges"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgovernance-badges.md:14
msgid ""
"**✓ Gevalideerd (green)** — the DMN has been officially validated. The "
"validating organisation and date are confirmed. This DMN has passed "
"technical quality assurance by a recognised authority and is appropriate for "
"production use."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgovernance-badges.md:16
msgid ""
"**⏱ In Review (amber)** — validation is in progress. The DMN has been "
"submitted to a competent authority but the review is not yet complete. Use "
"with caution in production environments; contact the publishing agency for "
"status."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgovernance-badges.md:18
msgid ""
"**No badge** — no validation record exists in TriplyDB for this DMN. It may "
"be experimental, a draft, or a community-contributed model. Verify its "
"suitability independently before use in production."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgovernance-badges.md:22
msgid "Hover tooltip"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgovernance-badges.md:24
msgid ""
"Hover over any badge to see full validation details: the name of the "
"validating organisation, the validation date in Dutch format, and any "
"validation note recorded by the publisher."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgovernance-badges.md:28
msgid "Using validated DMNs in a chain"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgovernance-badges.md:30
msgid ""
"Governance badges are visible both in the Available DMNs list and on cards "
"inside the Chain Composer. Building a chain from validated DMNs gives you "
"confidence that each decision in the chain has been reviewed by its "
"responsible authority."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgovernance-badges.md:34
msgid "Adding validation metadata (for publishers)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgovernance-badges.md:36
msgid ""
"Validation metadata is added when publishing a DMN to TriplyDB via the CPSV "
"Editor. In the CPSV Editor, expand the **Validation Status** section before "
"publishing and select the appropriate status. If the status is \"Officially "
"Validated\", fill in the validating organisation URI and validation date."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cuser-guide%5Cgovernance-badges.md:38
msgid ""
"For the full publishing workflow, see [CPSV Editor — Publishing to TriplyDB]"
"{1}."
msgstr ""
